#: 2021-01-05-citizens-assembly-climate-change.md:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DRWwaxTe6is\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
