#. type: Title ##
#: 2021-01-05-citizens-assembly-climate-change.md:155
#, no-wrap
msgid "CA case study: Climate Assembly UK"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2021-01-05-citizens-assembly-climate-change.md:158
msgid ""
"During six weekends between January and May 2020, the city of Birmingham in "
"England hosted [Climate Assembly UK](http://www.climateassembly.uk). Due to "
"COVID-19, the final two weekends were conducted online. The assembly was "
"requested by six ‘Select Committees’ (groups of UK Members of Parliament "
"from various political parties) representing business and energy strategy, "
"the environment, the treasury, housing, local government, science, "
"technology and transport."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2021-01-05-citizens-assembly-climate-change.md:160
msgid ""
"This assembly of 110 citizens concentrated on one element of the climate and "
"ecological crisis:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: 2021-01-05-citizens-assembly-climate-change.md:162
msgid "How can the UK reduce greenhouse gas emissions to net zero by 2050*?"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2021-01-05-citizens-assembly-climate-change.md:164
msgid "\\*Extinction Rebellion demands net zero by 2025"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2021-01-05-citizens-assembly-climate-change.md:166
msgid "![](/assets/uploads/f5f22775-22a0-4b3e-9efc-d0bc51221f9e.png)"
msgstr ""

